    },
    {
      "id": "OvWKsA5nJ7IexX26jU6oh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 527,
      "y": 227.5,
      "width": 443,
      "height": 52,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1566798847,
      "version": 238,
      "versionNonce": 1444657649,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1679909447986,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Le serveur HTML sert les fichiers statiques\n(front et admin) stockés sur le FileSystem",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 44,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Le serveur HTML sert les fichiers statiques\n(front et admin) stockés sur le FileSystem"
    },
    {
      "id": "L3BkbCBisuJpjrqCxa4OR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 556,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 471,
      "height": 104,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 133238065,
      "version": 846,
      "versionNonce": 1980357023,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1679909447986,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "L'API GraphQL lit/écrit dans la BDD les infos\ndes campagnes, enregistre les images uploadées\ndans le FileSystem uploads, sert les images et\ncommunique avec l'API SalesForces. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 96,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "L'API GraphQL lit/écrit dans la BDD les infos\ndes campagnes, enregistre les images uploadées\ndans le FileSystem uploads, sert les images et\ncommunique avec l'API SalesForces. "
    },
    {
      "type": "arrow",
      "version": 948,
